    "ExaCT uses a simple BoW representation.",
    "Finally, RobotReviewer/RobotSearch uses BoW for the linear model and an embedding layer for the CNN model.",
    "Table 4 provides an overview of the proportion of tools covering each of the 23 features.",
    "These features are categorised across the six categories outlined in Sect. 5.1.2.",
    "The Table in Appendix (Table 8) provides a more general analysis, detailing how the 21 tools address the 23 features."
